    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained ride? This vehicle is in good condition and ready to hit the road with its next owner! It has been cared for and shows only minor signs of use, making it a fantastic choice for anyone seeking quality and dependability. Come see why this smooth-running car is the perfect addition to your driveway!",
